@startuml
title Authentification JWT - Vue simplifiee

skinparam shadowing false
actor "Utilisateur" as User
participant "Angular" as Front
participant "API Spring Boot" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> Front : Email + mot de passe
Front -> API : POST /api/auth/login
API -> DB : Verifier utilisateur
DB --> API : Utilisateur valide
API -> API : Creer JWT + refresh token
API --> Front : AuthResponse
Front --> User : Acces au dashboard
@enduml
